caption.text:
Hi, announcement here!
After hearing feedbacks from friends (thanks so much!) I decided to make a new IG account for Mimi N art. It has no posts yet coz I made it like 1hr ago.

The username is futarinokizuna_

This IG account (sunpro_diary) will change its purpose into a ROLEPLAY acc (yes u heard it right, I'm crazy) of my next project. Yes, this acc is still art account but not as updated as new one, it is combined with some random daily stuff of my OC (it's my stuff actually). I have considered this since years ago and 2017 has come so I think it's time. I am currently rearranging this acc. Feel free to unfollow this random acc ans follow new one if u aren't into my private life.

TL;DR my new art acc is futarinokizuna_ 
this acc (sunpro_diary) is no longer mine.
if u are interested of doodle spams and kinda okay arts then follow me there. Please. See u soon!
P.S. I prefer to follow art account so I can't follow all of you. Sorry.

Heya I'm back!
For #InkTober 2016, I thought it will be boring if they are just.... illustrations. I mean I nearly lost my motivation last year :p so this year it will be more challenging: a SILENT COMIC (yes coz I didn't join sma06 contest) but what is this comic about? Nothing really. It's random daily comic about 2ppl who happened to have same face and are very close (?) Not an adventure or drama something. So I hope it's interesting and you enjoy it! Happy Inktober! #inktober #inktoberid #inktober2016
